# Architecture Drift Check

Before and after implementation:

1. Read `docs/architecture/ARCHITECTURE_BASELINE.md`.
2. Run checklist in `docs/architecture/ARCHITECTURE_DRIFT_CHECK.md`.
3. If drift is detected, document in PLAN or create an ADR under `docs/decisions/`.

Key invariants:

- Controller → Service → Mapper layering
- Agent Tool → Service (never Mapper directly)
- Backend owns all AI API calls
- RAG answers include sources
- Agent execution writes trace
